  / Footer Notice
  .mt-12.pt-6.border-t-2.border-gray-300
    %p.text-sm.text-gray-700.text-center.leading-relaxed
      %strong By accepting this agreement, you confirm your understanding and acceptance of all terms and conditions set forth in this B2B Partnership Agreement with Wheelsonrent-FZCO.
      This agreement is governed by the laws of the United Arab Emirates.
